frames.caption: An enigmatic figure stands in a misty forest, draped in layered, tattered robes. Her glowing eyes and the mysterious cauldron-like object beside her create an eerie atmosphere. The dimly lit cottage in the background adds to the mystical setting.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mysterious, possibly magical figure in a foggy forest setting. The presence of a rustic cottage and peculiar mushrooms enhances the fantastical ambiance.

frames.caption: An enigmatic figure stands in a misty forest, draped in a tattered cloak with glowing eyes. She holds a large, ornate cauldron with one hand, surrounded by vibrant mushrooms. A rustic cabin with warm, glowing windows is visible in the background.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mystical forest, shrouded in fog. The central figure, possibly a witch, exudes an aura of mystery and power. The environment is both eerie and enchanting, with a sense of ancient magic.
